p:
Colorado domestic cat samples were collected from free-ranging cats on entry to shelters close to the FR and WS regions in Colorado. Two shelters in Boulder (Boulder Humane Society and Community Cat Care Shelter) and one in Ridgway (Ridgway Second Chance Shelter) provided samples as previously described (
 Bevins et al. 2012; 
 Carver et al. 2016). Australian domestic cat blood samples were opportunistically collected by the Beatty Lab at The University of Sydney, from pet domestic cats following routine clinical care at the university Veterinary Teaching Hospital.
